          Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Quasi quo
          animi id culpa maiores illo incidunt aliquid necessitatibus iusto
          ipsum dolorem, quos eum, eos dolore laudantium? Minima quidem
          repudiandae officiis.
        </p>
      </figcaption>
      <div class="flex w-2/5">
        <div class="w-1/3 pt-64">
          <div class="p-2">
            <div
              class="relative pb-[125%] rounded-xl shadow-xl overflow-hidden"
            >
              <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 h-full w-full">
                <Img src="/images/foods-and-drinks/hero-bg.jpg" alt="" />
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="w-1/3 pt-32">
          <div class="p-2">
